parameters: Huh, an empty marble pedestal. The Goddess statue from the third dungeon was standing on one of these, but this one is empty. Was that because you couldn’t save the last one? You wonder where this one ran off to\..\..\..
\u[48,0]Yeah, whatever do you think happened to her?
Would you like to fight the corrupted Goddess again?

Alternatively, if you \fidon’t\fi defeat the Minotaur, she’ll probably come gloat while you’re filled up with bull cock, which would be rather humiliating\..\..\..
